FBIS3-18393 "drweu041_p_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-041 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Mar 1994 GREECE Spokesman Comments on FYROM Initiatives NC0103132494 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1230 GMT 1 Mar 94 NC0103132494 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] Answering a question, government spokesman Evangelos Venizelos said the Greek Government does not know whether UN mediator Cyrus Vance will meet Skopjean officials after meeting Foreign Minister Karolos Papoulias in Geneva on 10 March. He added that with this meeting, the Greek side will be given the opportunity to explain in detail its positions following the measures against Skopje. Asked whether there is an initiative on Skopje [The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia--FYROM] by European Commission President Jacques Delors, Venizelos said: We have Dutch European Union Commissioner Hans Van Den Broek's political mission and Delors' letter to Prime Minister Andreas Papandreou.
